compute_word_loss[source]

compute_word_loss(img_features, words_emb, cap_len, gamma1=4.0, gamma2=5.0, gamma3=10.0)

img_features(context): batch x emb_sz x 17 x 17 words_emb(query): batch x seq_len x emb_sz
